These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, satire
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, cricket
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, bike
1. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
2. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
3. the person watching satire movies is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | iced-tea   |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | documentary   |
| Sport         | cricket | tennis |
| Transport     | trike | bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, cherry
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: family, martial-arts
2 different pets are kept: pony, fish
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, boat
1. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching family movies is the person driving the boat##1
3. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | pepper     | cherry |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | family  |
| Pet           | fish         | pony     |
| Transport     | car   | boat    |

 #################################

 
