.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, 7up
There 2 different types of food: carrot, pineapple
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, board-games
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, reggae
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the fan of reggae is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | 7up     | fanta |
| Food          | pineapple   | carrot  |
| Hobby         | camping | board-games     |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | reggae         |

