.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  lawyer, manager
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, american
2 different pets are kept: turtle, ferret
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
2. the american is on the far left or far right##3
3. the manager is the turkish##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | manager | lawyer    |
| Nationality   | turkish       | american |
| Pet           | turtle         | ferret    |
| Sport         | swimming    | badminton   |

